Nigerian singing sensation Davido is overjoyed about becoming a father for the third time. Davido and his fiancé Chioma Rowland welcomed their lil prince into the world last Sunday. The singer gushed over his queen, labelling her a “strong wife”. He also revealed that they've named their son David Adedeji Adeleke Jr. Davido popped the question to Chioma surrounded by family and friends last month. He shared a snap of the gorg pear-shaped diamond ring he got for her on Instagram.